d get </span><span class=\"s2\">little</span><span class=\"s1\"> result out of it. It creates scenarios where everything seems to be against you. It pushes you to your limits to a point where you feel you can’t go any further. </span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">How comfortable would life be if everything was handed out to us on a golden platter. If everything in our life fell right into place and was within our comfort zone. If life handed us situations exactly when we needed them in the best possible scenario. If life would just be a bed of roses. Right?</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">WRONG.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">What most of us fail to realise is that life is not a bed of roses and it never can be. You cannot be born with a silver spoon and expect to lead a life with the same level of ease. Opportunities won’t be given to you in your hand. You have to work hard. Work hard to prove that you are better than the other million people competing with you out there. Work hard to prove you love what you’re doing and you want it badly. Work hard to prove you deserve what you get.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Hardships are a part of life.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The more challenges you face, the better you become and handling them. The more problems you encounter, the better you become at finding a solution. The more mistakes you make, the better you become at rectifying them. Every step in life, every hardship we face, every action of ours teaches us something. It teaches us valuable life lessons that simply cannot be taught in the classroom, in the boardroom or anywhere else. These are lessons that teach you to be human. To be compassionate. To be responsible. </span></p>\n&nbsp;\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Every little failure brings us a step closer. One step closer to our ultimate goal. One step closer to our horizon.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The world today is amazing. It constantly challenges you to do things you are not comfortable with. It forces you to work hard to get </span><span class=\"s3\">little</span><span class=\"s1\">, but a satisfying result out of it. It creates scenarios where everything seems to be against you. It pushes you to your limits to a point where you feel you can’t go any further. </span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">But you can. You can go further. That’s the perplexing charm.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The world forces you to think out of the box and face situations you never thought you were capable of facing. It teaches you to deal with unexpected failure and overjoying success, sometimes both at the same time. It encourages you to grow as a person. </span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Life is beautiful. It won\'t always be happy. It will be hard, really hard. But that doesn\'t mean you\'ll run away. No. You\'ll stay and fight for what you want, for what you deserve. And in the end, you\'ll be happy. If you\'re not happy, it’s not the end.</span></p>','','','draft','open','open','','','','','2017-11-04 13:27:37','2017-11-04 13:27:37','',0,'https://iiitd.ecell.io/blog/?p=66',0,'post','',0),(85,5,'2018-05-10 08:36:14','2018-05-10 08:36:14','<p> Miljoenen mensen haten het gratis om regelmatig fulltime bij werken. Dit betekent niets dat ze niet over werk houden. Het ben precies het tegenovergestelde plus ze opereren liever hard om hun bijzonder kantoor tot en met beslist succes te herzien. </p>  <p> Er is enorme aantallen die hen tijd  op ie werk willen doorbrengen plus dromen ervan vrij binnenshuis zijn betreffende de noodzaak om dus vaste baan te hebben. Het ben zeker verrassend populair tijdverdrijf. Daarom spenderen zij regelmatig tijdsbestek in het surfen op internet, op zoek volgens full-time inkomstenmogelijkheden die hen huidige parcours moeten vernieuwen. </p>  <p> Dit is niets de beste aanpak. Wanneer gevolg betreffende de popula